body_html:
Trivial benchmark on my machine:

import torch

x = torch.randn(5)
y = torch.randn(5)

for i in range(1000000):
    x *= y

Before:

real	0m1.434s
user	0m1.385s
sys	0m0.028s

After:

real	0m1.131s
user	0m1.103s
sys	0m0.029s

    x *= y

real	0m1.434s
